<HEAD>Man Allegedly Marries Nine Women, Forces Them Into Prostitution</HEAD>
<DATELINE>KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A man married nine women in
Thailand and then forced them to become prostitutes in Malaysia,
the national news agency Bernama reported Sunday.
   It quoted senior Moslem clergyman Abdul Mutalib Mohamed as
